    {
      "kind": "parameters",
      "languages": [
        "swift"
      ],
      "parameters": [
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The run loop mode to run. ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "mode",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " can be any arbitrary CFString. You do not need to explicitly create a run loop mode, although a run loop mode needs to contain at least one source or timer to run. ",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "mode"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "The length of time to run the run loop. If ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "0",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": ", only one pass is made through the run loop before returning; if multiple sources or timers are ready to fire immediately, only one (possibly two if one is a version 0 source) will be fired, regardless of the value of ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "returnAfterSourceHandled",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": ".",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "seconds"
        },
        {
          "content": [
            {
              "inlineContent": [
                {
                  "text": "A flag indicating whether the run loop should exit after processing one source. If ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "false",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": ", the run loop continues processing events until ",
                  "type": "text"
                },
                {
                  "code": "seconds",
                  "type": "codeVoice"
                },
                {
                  "text": " has passed.",
                  "type": "text"
                }
              ],
              "type": "paragraph"
            }
          ],
          "name": "returnAfterSourceHandled"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "return_value",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Return Value",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A value indicating the reason the run loop exited. Possible values are described below.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    },
    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Run loops can be run recursively. You can call ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1541988-cfrunloopruninmode",
              "isActive": false,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " from within any run loop callout and create nested run loop activations on the current thread’s call stack. You are not restricted in which modes you can run from within a callout. You can create another run loop activation running in any available run loop mode, including any modes already running higher in the call stack.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "The run loop exits with the following return values under the indicated conditions:",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "items": [
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "kCFRunLoopRunFinished",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". The run loop mode ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "mode",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " has no sources or timers.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "kCFRunLoopRunStopped",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". The run loop was stopped with ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/1541796-cfrunloopstop",
                      "isActive": true,
                      "type": "reference"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "kCFRunLoopRunTimedOut",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". The time interval ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "seconds",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " passed.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "content": [
                {
                  "inlineContent": [
                    {
                      "code": "kCFRunLoopRunHandledSource",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ". A source was processed. This exit condition only applies when ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "returnAfterSourceHandled",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": " is ",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "code": "true",
                      "type": "codeVoice"
                    },
                    {
                      "text": ".",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          ],
          "type": "unorderedList"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You must not specify the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/corefoundation/cfrunloopmode/1542364-commonmodes",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " constant for the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "mode",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": " parameter. Run loops always run in a specific mode. You specify the common modes only when configuring a run-loop observer and only in situations where you want that observer to run in more than one mode.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
